# Gameplay scripts

- Names: `XxxDefinition` (SO), `XxxRuntime` (sim), `XxxView` (MonoBehaviour).
- Gems: `GemId` switch factory → `IAttackModifier`; no reflection.
- Services constructed in `GameCompositionRoot`; Gameplay must not reference UI or Steam assemblies.
- Balance only via ScriptableObject fields.
